Commentary: is he run out here? This looks very tight! The ball is tucked into the leg side, and they push hard for a second run. But the throw from the deep is a good one, as is the take from Mushfiqur. He collects it in front of the stumps, whipping his gloves back in a flash to disturb the stumps with Madhevere just short of his ground. Bangladesh have a third strike inside the Powerplay, and they're bossing this
